# Protocol 26: Agent Proceed Confirmation (AGENT-PROCEED-CONF)

> **Normative:** `gtcx-docs/docs/governance/protocols/26-agent-proceed-confirmation/protocol.md` (v1.1.0)
> **Phase:** 5.6 (after P22 selection)

## Rule

After `pnpm agent:next-work`, emit **one Proceed Brief**, then **implement**. Human may **stop**, **correct**, or name a story ID — never pick among agent-generated options.

## Hard-forbidden replies (never send)

- Your call / Your call on …
- Two options / 1. … 2. … (story, repo, or sprint menus)
- Since blockers are done, natural transition point → menu
- Either IR-X in infra or switch to compliance-os now
- Which do you prefer? / What would you like me to do next?

## With P27

Run commands yourself after the brief — no terminal delegation.
